1
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:35,940
=The Embroidered Truth=

2
00:00:38,119 --> 00:00:39,359
Dare to report me, huh?

3
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:42,399
Your greedy parents sent you to me.

4
00:00:42,880 --> 00:00:45,200
Aren't they marrying you off well?

5
00:00:46,439 --> 00:00:49,200
If you serve me obediently,

6
00:00:49,679 --> 00:00:51,799
I might just keep you around.

7
00:00:52,039 --> 00:00:53,280
Dare to report me again,

8
00:00:53,600 --> 00:00:55,759
I'll let all of Jinxiu City know

9
00:00:55,960 --> 00:00:57,000
that you, a shameless slut,

10
00:00:57,000 --> 00:00:58,280
seduced me.

11
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,200
Master.

12
00:01:12,439 --> 00:01:14,400
Lin Rulan jumped off the building.

13
00:01:24,180 --> 00:01:28,180
=Episode 2=

14
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:38,640
Master.

15
00:01:38,840 --> 00:01:39,959
What's wrong with you?

16
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:42,040
She's back.

17
00:01:42,680 --> 00:01:43,879
Who's back?

18
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,079
Lin Rulan.

19
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:48,719
Lin Rulan?

20
00:01:48,840 --> 00:01:50,319
Didn't she already die?

21
00:01:52,599 --> 00:01:53,680
She's alive.

22
00:01:56,239 --> 00:01:58,200
This is getting interesting.

23
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,719
Your Highness!

24
00:02:02,780 --> 00:02:04,680
(Xiaojiu,
Lady Cheng'en's Personal Guard)

25
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:05,480
Your Highness.

26
00:02:05,599 --> 00:02:06,519
Forgive me for barging in.

27
00:02:06,799 --> 00:02:07,920
My Lady, she...

28
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:09,520
She's threatening to hang herself!

29
00:02:12,199 --> 00:02:14,360
My Lady,
Her Highness is here to see you.

30
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,199
Just let me die!

31
00:02:17,280 --> 00:02:18,120
My Lady!

32
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:19,919
How can I show my face again?

33
00:02:19,919 --> 00:02:20,400
My Lady!

34
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,039
Ruoheng.

35
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,439
What's the matter with you?

36
00:02:23,039 --> 00:02:23,800
Wenyue.

37
00:02:24,879 --> 00:02:27,400
I only asked that merchant
to measure my sizes.

38
00:02:27,479 --> 00:02:30,000
But he insulted me and stormed off.

39
00:02:30,319 --> 00:02:31,879
I am a noble lady,

40
00:02:31,919 --> 00:02:32,800
yet he dared to...

41
00:02:33,439 --> 00:02:35,400
How can I show my face again?

42
00:02:35,520 --> 00:02:37,199
Master Wu's skills are unmatched.

43
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:39,039
He's just a bit arrogant.

44
00:02:39,199 --> 00:02:41,800
He'd never dare act up in this manor.

45
00:02:41,879 --> 00:02:43,680
Perhaps
since you arrived in Jinxiu City,

46
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:45,400
you've had some misunderstandings.

47
00:02:45,919 --> 00:02:48,759
Master Wu only tailors for Her Highness.

48
00:02:48,919 --> 00:02:51,400
He may not know how to serve others.

49
00:02:57,840 --> 00:03:00,919
You know me well, Wenyue.

50
00:03:01,280 --> 00:03:02,400
I've always been proud and stubborn.

51
00:03:02,439 --> 00:03:04,240
Except for you,

52
00:03:04,240 --> 00:03:05,800
I've never bowed to anyone.

53
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:06,400
But he...

54
00:03:06,400 --> 00:03:07,240
I know your temperament

55
00:03:07,240 --> 00:03:08,759
better than anyone.

56
00:03:08,840 --> 00:03:11,800
Wu Lian must have displeased you
with his words.

57
00:03:12,080 --> 00:03:14,319
Don't stoop to his level.

58
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:17,800
Do you still remember?

59
00:03:18,039 --> 00:03:19,919
You've always protected me like this.

60
00:03:20,080 --> 00:03:22,280
Never letting anyone bully me.

61
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:23,319
Don't worry, Ruoheng.

62
00:03:24,000 --> 00:03:26,000
If Wu Lian really disrespected you

63
00:03:26,000 --> 00:03:27,439
and made you unhappy,

64
00:03:27,479 --> 00:03:29,000
I will stand up for you.

65
00:03:30,080 --> 00:03:31,719
Master! Master!

66
00:03:31,719 --> 00:03:32,560
Master!

67
00:03:33,919 --> 00:03:34,560
Shut up!

68
00:03:35,719 --> 00:03:36,520
My Lady.

69
00:03:36,800 --> 00:03:38,400
Her Highness still protects Wu Lian.

70
00:03:38,520 --> 00:03:40,000
For our revenge, I...

71
00:03:40,639 --> 00:03:41,360
It doesn't matter.

72
00:03:41,520 --> 00:03:42,800
This was just a test.

73
00:03:43,680 --> 00:03:46,400
Now, I see where her loyalties lie.

74
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:48,159
But Wu Lian won't let this go.

75
00:03:48,680 --> 00:03:50,439
He'll definitely seek revenge.

76
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:54,879
Xiaotao.

77
00:03:55,039 --> 00:03:55,719
It's fine.

78
00:03:56,039 --> 00:03:57,319
Our allies are waiting outside.

79
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:59,479
We'll hear from your sister soon.

80
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:03,199
Master.

81
00:04:03,800 --> 00:04:04,680
The Princess Consort orders you

82
00:04:04,879 --> 00:04:06,479
to see her in the manor at once.

83
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:08,800
Understood.

84
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:28,439
Bad luck.

85
00:04:37,300 --> 00:04:40,300
(Mengqiu Pavilion)

86
00:04:41,920 --> 00:04:43,600
You never should have messed with her.

87
00:04:49,439 --> 00:04:50,759
I made Lady Cheng'en misunderstand me.

88
00:04:51,639 --> 00:04:53,000
It was never my intention.

89
00:04:53,240 --> 00:04:55,560
I don't care about your intentions.

90
00:04:56,839 --> 00:05:00,639
It's time you tamed your temper.

91
00:05:01,920 --> 00:05:04,319
The things you've done in the past,

92
00:05:04,519 --> 00:05:06,399
I've heard rumors about them.

93
00:05:06,839 --> 00:05:08,480
I chose to look the other way.

94
00:05:09,519 --> 00:05:10,639
But now,

95
00:05:11,399 --> 00:05:13,000
things are different.

96
00:05:13,199 --> 00:05:14,920
If you provoke her again,

97
00:05:14,920 --> 00:05:16,360
I won't spare you.

98
00:05:16,680 --> 00:05:17,480
Your Highness.

99
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,639
She's your cousin.

100
00:05:20,199 --> 00:05:21,839
Even if I don't care for her,

101
00:05:22,000 --> 00:05:23,399
I must respect your wishes.

102
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,720
Please forgive me, Your Highness.

103
00:05:27,800 --> 00:05:29,199
Since you understand,

104
00:05:29,439 --> 00:05:31,000
I won't say more.

105
00:05:31,240 --> 00:05:32,720
Before the Prince returns,

106
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,360
stay out of trouble.

107
00:05:52,199 --> 00:05:52,920
Master.

108
00:05:53,399 --> 00:05:55,480
I've had Luoxia arrange everything.

109
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:58,680
We can use the Princess Consort

110
00:05:58,720 --> 00:05:59,759
to get rid of her.

111
00:06:00,000 --> 00:06:02,480
Faking royal blood is a capital crime.

112
00:06:03,399 --> 00:06:05,120
If I don't fan the flames,

113
00:06:05,600 --> 00:06:07,680
this fire will never catch on.

114
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:12,279
Take care of her first.

115
00:06:14,000 --> 00:06:16,000
Then deal with her accomplices.

116
00:06:18,600 --> 00:06:19,399
Meng Wan.

117
00:06:20,399 --> 00:06:23,000
Why are you staring at Lady Cheng'en
like that?

118
00:06:23,839 --> 00:06:24,879
Forgive me, Master.

119
00:06:25,879 --> 00:06:28,079
Her Ladyship's face reminds me

120
00:06:28,319 --> 00:06:30,360
of someone I used to know.

121
00:06:30,800 --> 00:06:32,000
I couldn't help but look.

122
00:06:32,839 --> 00:06:34,680
Do you know who she is?

123
00:06:35,040 --> 00:06:36,759
Your "friend" is not worthy.

124
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:40,279
I let my memories cloud my judgment.

125
00:06:40,319 --> 00:06:41,399
I overstepped.

126
00:06:41,639 --> 00:06:43,319
Please punish me, My Lady.

127
00:06:45,480 --> 00:06:46,360
Rise.

128
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,199
Thank you, My Lady.

129
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:51,319
(Luoxia, Jingyuan Manor's Maid)
Master Wu embroiders plants beautifully.

130
00:06:51,720 --> 00:06:53,879
These orchids are especially lifelike.

131
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:55,839
What a pity.

132
00:06:56,120 --> 00:06:57,680
There was once someone in my shop

133
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:59,279
who embroidered perfect orchids too.

134
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:02,920
If she were still alive,

135
00:07:04,000 --> 00:07:05,600
she'd have no place to go now.

136
00:07:06,519 --> 00:07:08,199
You're joking again, Master Wu.

137
00:07:08,639 --> 00:07:09,600
If she's not a person,

138
00:07:09,839 --> 00:07:11,160
is she a ghost then?

139
00:07:18,079 --> 00:07:18,879
Ruoheng.

140
00:07:21,839 --> 00:07:23,000
I'm fine, Wenyue.

141
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:25,160
I just feel a bit of

142
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:26,759
tightness in my chest.

143
00:07:27,839 --> 00:07:29,079
Her Ladyship's palpitations
are acting up.

144
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,199
She needs to rest and take medicine.

145
00:07:30,680 --> 00:07:32,360
Help her to her room at once.

146
00:07:40,600 --> 00:07:41,399
Your Highness.

147
00:07:42,720 --> 00:07:44,279
His Highness will be back soon.

148
00:07:46,279 --> 00:07:47,600
Her Ladyship is frail.

149
00:07:48,399 --> 00:07:50,240
She can't help you secure favor.

150
00:07:51,519 --> 00:07:52,319
Luoxia.

151
00:07:52,959 --> 00:07:54,519
Wait outside her room.

152
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,360
When she feels better,

153
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,879
let me know.

154
00:07:58,240 --> 00:07:59,040
Yes, Your Highness.

155
00:08:08,120 --> 00:08:10,000
Are you feeling better?

156
00:08:10,399 --> 00:08:12,160
You're new to Jinxiu City,

157
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,319
you must be feeling unwell
from the journey.

158
00:08:14,439 --> 00:08:17,000
I had the kitchen make some snacks.

159
00:08:17,240 --> 00:08:18,519
Please try some.

160
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:28,000
Forgive me, My Lady!

161
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:30,399
Luoxia, you're getting careless.

162
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:31,439
Oh no!

163
00:08:31,639 --> 00:08:33,000
Ruoheng is allergic to peach blossoms.

164
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,240
Are you alright, My Lady?

165
00:08:37,399 --> 00:08:38,200
Your Highness.

166
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:40,519
My Lady is
severely allergic to peach blossoms.

167
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,519
When this happens at home,

168
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:44,120
sleeping helps her recover.

169
00:08:44,279 --> 00:08:46,279
Rest well then, Ruoheng.

170
00:08:46,399 --> 00:08:47,639
I'll leave you to it.

171
00:08:57,080 --> 00:08:58,039
I was too hasty.

172
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,399
I almost exposed myself.

173
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,000
Thankfully, you reacted quickly.

174
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,360
Otherwise...

175
00:09:06,120 --> 00:09:06,919
Your Highness.

176
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:08,960
I have  urgent news.

177
00:09:09,639 --> 00:09:14,919
I suspect Lady Cheng'en is not
who she claims to be.

178
00:09:15,639 --> 00:09:17,639
Where did you hear such nonsense?

179
00:09:18,240 --> 00:09:19,879
I heard it from no one.

180
00:09:20,639 --> 00:09:24,200
She's the daughter of Lord Cheng'en

181
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,919
but willing to be a concubine...

182
00:09:26,080 --> 00:09:27,200
That's rare.

183
00:09:27,639 --> 00:09:30,480
But you chose her for His Highness.

184
00:09:31,279 --> 00:09:33,519
If she's not a virgin,

185
00:09:34,000 --> 00:09:37,200
you'll be the one in trouble.

186
00:09:39,840 --> 00:09:41,519
It's kind of you to worry.

187
00:09:41,799 --> 00:09:42,600
I'll think about it.

188
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,360
You may leave.

189
00:09:45,279 --> 00:09:46,080
Yes, Your Highness.

190
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,639
What did Wu Lian mean by that?

191
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:57,960
Could it be...?

192
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:00,799
From what he implied,

193
00:10:01,720 --> 00:10:05,519
Lady Cheng'en may no longer be a virgin.

194
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:10,159
Keep her confined to her courtyard.

195
00:10:10,279 --> 00:10:11,320
She is not to leave.

196
00:10:12,240 --> 00:10:13,519
Send for Nanny He.

197
00:10:13,679 --> 00:10:16,279
Verify her virginity tomorrow.

198
00:10:16,519 --> 00:10:17,759
If she is not a virgin,

199
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:20,320
she will be drowned
in the pond immediately.

200
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:56,960
♪Night fades before the dawn♪

201
00:10:57,200 --> 00:11:00,200
♪Old vows still guide my hand♪

202
00:11:01,400 --> 00:11:04,160
♪The past no longer binds♪

203
00:11:04,640 --> 00:11:08,360
♪My heart still shines through dust♪

204
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:12,920
♪Silent blooms, unchanged heart♪

205
00:11:13,760 --> 00:11:16,640
♪Bare hands weave through the frost♪

206
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,000
♪Shadows linger, rain returns♪

207
00:11:19,000 --> 00:11:23,080
♪Honor crowns my weary soul♪

208
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:25,680
♪For your faith that never broke♪

209
00:11:25,880 --> 00:11:30,000
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

210
00:11:30,880 --> 00:11:32,800
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

211
00:11:32,800 --> 00:11:37,040
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

212
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:40,720
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

213
00:11:40,840 --> 00:11:43,480
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

214
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:46,080
♪One thought turns into ash♪

215
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:52,400
♪No future left to write♪

216
00:11:53,480 --> 00:11:55,280
♪If I never fall♪

217
00:11:55,320 --> 00:11:57,680
♪How could this waiting end♪

218
00:11:57,680 --> 00:11:59,040
♪If I bear no scars♪

219
00:11:59,040 --> 00:12:01,360
♪How could I challenge fate♪

220
00:12:01,360 --> 00:12:03,720
♪I knew there was no way back♪

221
00:12:03,720 --> 00:12:07,720
♪Yet I left this hope behind♪

222
00:12:07,840 --> 00:12:09,960
♪For your faith that never broke♪

223
00:12:10,160 --> 00:12:14,120
♪I shattered all the love I knew♪

224
00:12:15,080 --> 00:12:17,000
♪No regrets, no debts unpaid♪

225
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:21,400
♪At dusk I walk away alone♪

226
00:12:22,480 --> 00:12:25,080
♪If this tale becomes a storm♪

227
00:12:25,120 --> 00:12:27,680
♪Old shadows fade from sight♪

228
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:30,040
♪One thought turns into ash♪

229
00:12:31,160 --> 00:12:36,400
♪No future left to write♪

230
00:12:37,280 --> 00:12:39,680
♪The lamp is out, you're gone♪

231
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:43,080
♪Heaven and earth fall silent♪

232
00:12:44,760 --> 00:12:46,960
♪If we meet again someday♪

233
00:12:47,400 --> 00:12:53,200
♪This longing sleeps beneath the snow♪
